---
title: Creamy Cajun Chicken Pasta with spinach and cheese
description: Chicken is an ingredient that's often used in Cajun cuisine. Less often utilized might be rigatoni—but that's just part of the beauty of this creamy, Cajun spiced fusion pasta dish.
